HEADWORD: Groundless
<hw>Ground"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>grundle⟦aacute⟧s</ets> bottomless.]</ety> <def>Without ground or
foundation; wanting cause or reason for support; not authorized; false;
baseless; <as>as, <ex>groundless</ex> fear; a <ex>groundless</ex>
report, rumor, or assertion.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Ground"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Ground"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms></p>

